                           <note>There are 133 miracles. All of them are numbered; the numbers are written in
                              the margins. Some miracles conclude with an extended, rhymed supplication
                              for the commissioner and scribe (<locus target="#27rc #29rc #38ra #52va"/>, <locus from="28rc" to="28va"/>,  <locus from="31rc" to="31va"/>, <locus from="44rb" to="44rc"/>,  <locus target="58rc" to="58va"/>).</note>
